data.description: HUGE REDUCTION! Motivated Seller! Charming & Spacious 3/2.5 townhome at "Florence @ Crystal Lakes" community. Mint condition. Immaculate thru-out featuring updated kitchen with Granite tops, Wooden cabinetry & SS appliances overlooking family/dining rooms. All fully tiled throughout & laminate, waterproof flooring on 2nd level. Zebra & blackout shades on all windows & sliding doors. 1 CG. Accordion shutters throughout. Good layout. Half bathroom downstairs has additional, hidden storage space. Spacious master suite has sitting area w/outside balcony access. Master bathroom features dual sinks & separate tub/shower. Large walk-in closet. Laundry room on 2nd level. Unique back patio has enclosed, covered area added by owner. Well-maintained community with Low HOA fees! Will not last!!
